<paragraph id="25603698FFE5FFEEE2C2A577CA297493" blockId="11.[151,1436,1773,2016]" lastBlockId="12.[151,1437,150,574]" lastPageId="12" lastPageNumber="313" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFE5FFE9E2C2A577CFF67341" bold="true" box="[199,438,1809,1835]" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">Emended diagnosis.</emphasis>
May be distinguished from other genera of 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFE5FFE9E1A2A577CA187341" authorityName="Navas" authorityYear="1910" box="[935,1112,1809,1835]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Nothochrysinae">Nothochrysinae</taxonomicName>
by a combination of the following. Forewing: (1) 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFE5FFE9E392A550CFF37325" box="[407,435,1846,1871]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">im</emphasis>
broad, pentagonal [
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFE5FFE9E090A553CD0F7325" authorityName="Wilmann" authorityYear="1993" box="[661,847,1845,1871]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Stephenbrooksia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFE5FFE9E090A553CD0F7325" box="[661,847,1845,1871]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">Stephenbrooksia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: very long, narrow; 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFE5FFE9E63DA553CAA07325" authorityName="Adams" authorityYear="1967" box="[1080,1248,1845,1871]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="312" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFE5FFE9E63DA553CAA07325" box="[1080,1248,1845,1871]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="312">Archaeochrysa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
